WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.980
[Episode 24]

02:54.910 --> 02:57.520
Qi Feng was hurt by the evil insect in order to save me.

02:58.690 --> 02:59.560
Don't blame yourself.

03:00.970 --> 03:02.170
I will find a way to save him.

03:06.500 --> 03:07.170
Master.

03:07.560 --> 03:08.810
There's nothing in this box.

03:10.000 --> 03:12.100
The evil insect really has come back to life.

03:12.530 --> 03:14.060
Maybe it was not dead at all.

03:14.390 --> 03:15.670
It just had been pretending to be dead.

03:28.490 --> 03:29.140
This is...

03:31.600 --> 03:32.870
Qi Feng has the same blood hole

03:32.870 --> 03:34.079
as that on Mr. Cang Sr.

03:35.110 --> 03:36.180
If I find out

03:36.350 --> 03:37.840
who used this evil insect to harm people,

03:38.810 --> 03:40.540
I will tear him into pieces.

03:44.130 --> 03:44.890
Cang Shan,

03:45.470 --> 03:47.190
go see if your mother is back.

03:47.210 --> 03:48.140
Invite her here.

03:48.170 --> 03:49.079
I have something to ask her.

03:53.740 --> 03:55.360
Why don't you just extract the evil insect?

03:56.150 --> 03:57.030
I can't.

03:59.730 --> 04:02.010
Then... why could the evil insect in Chief's body

04:02.030 --> 04:03.380
be extracted?

04:03.490 --> 04:05.170
Because Chief is dead.

04:05.690 --> 04:07.110
It can't be extracted

04:07.500 --> 04:08.660
unless the host is dead.

04:09.050 --> 04:10.340
How should we save Qi Feng?

04:24.100 --> 04:26.130
I've protected his heart and meridians with my demonic power.

04:26.840 --> 04:28.910
The evil insect can't kill him for the time being.

04:28.940 --> 04:29.820
Master.

04:29.840 --> 04:30.600
Bai Shuo.

04:30.720 --> 04:32.050
My mother hasn't come back yet.

04:34.210 --> 04:34.970
Cang Shan,

04:35.000 --> 04:36.530
you stay here and take care of Qi Feng.

04:36.720 --> 04:38.320
The clansmen still have some misunderstanding of you.

04:38.340 --> 04:39.630
You shouldn't walk around.

04:39.659 --> 04:40.450
Fan Yue and I are going

04:40.470 --> 04:41.270
to find your mother.

04:41.659 --> 04:42.750
My mother will be fine.

04:43.140 --> 04:43.760
Right?

04:44.060 --> 04:45.030
No matter what,

04:45.610 --> 04:47.760
I will do everything I can to minimize the damage the murderer

04:47.790 --> 04:48.690
has inflicted on the Stone Clan.

05:00.330 --> 05:02.060
Father, what are you doing?

05:02.690 --> 05:03.550
I'm not leaving.

05:03.580 --> 05:05.070
-What are you doing?
-Hurry up!

05:05.450 --> 05:06.200
Father,

05:06.230 --> 05:07.160
can you tell me

05:07.180 --> 05:08.250
what on earth happened?

05:08.280 --> 05:09.400
Why are we suddenly leaving the Stone Clan?

05:09.430 --> 05:10.300
Don't ask.

05:10.320 --> 05:10.840
I'm your father.

05:10.870 --> 05:11.920
I won't harm you.

05:11.940 --> 05:12.620
We must leave now.

05:12.650 --> 05:13.400
I'm not leaving.

05:13.600 --> 05:14.950
If you don't tell me why,

05:14.970 --> 05:15.940
I won't go anywhere.

05:15.970 --> 05:16.410
You...

05:16.720 --> 05:17.990
Chief is already dead.

05:18.510 --> 05:19.880
You are an elder of our clan.

05:19.900 --> 05:20.700
If you leave,

05:20.730 --> 05:21.970
what about the clansmen?

05:23.410 --> 05:25.080
We should leave as soon as possible

05:25.100 --> 05:26.990
just because Chief is dead.

05:27.380 --> 05:28.620
Didn't you say

05:28.810 --> 05:30.650
Chief was killed by Cang Shan?

05:30.760 --> 05:32.290
Are you afraid of Cang Shan?

05:32.570 --> 05:33.440
Or...

05:34.159 --> 05:34.900
Father,

05:35.409 --> 05:36.450
are you afraid

05:36.720 --> 05:37.850
of someone else?

05:40.580 --> 05:42.960
I watched Cang Shan grow up.

05:42.990 --> 05:45.040
How could I not know his nature?

05:45.060 --> 05:46.300
He would never kill his father!

05:46.330 --> 05:47.770
But you wanted to kill him in front

05:47.800 --> 05:48.430
of the clansmen!

05:48.450 --> 05:50.730
I did that to show the real murderer!

05:51.830 --> 05:52.890
Anyway, there should be no delay.

05:52.909 --> 05:53.780
Come with me now!

06:11.790 --> 06:13.190
Young Chief, who are you waiting for?

06:14.980 --> 06:15.650
Sir.

06:17.050 --> 06:18.050
You're finally awake.

06:18.990 --> 06:19.750
How are you feeling?

06:19.780 --> 06:21.580
Do you feel uncomfortable?

06:22.080 --> 06:22.770
No.

06:22.950 --> 06:23.820
I'm fine.

06:24.910 --> 06:25.910
Master injected

06:25.930 --> 06:27.050
demonic power into your body

06:27.080 --> 06:28.190
to protect your heart and meridians.

06:28.210 --> 06:29.440
You'll be fine for the time being.

06:29.930 --> 06:31.200
Yue is so nice to me.

06:32.460 --> 06:33.620
I've been lying in bed for too long.

06:34.110 --> 06:35.480
My body is a little stiff.

06:35.820 --> 06:37.060
Can you do me a favor?

06:37.080 --> 06:38.790
Put me in the wheelchair.

06:42.280 --> 06:43.300
It's cold at night.

06:43.330 --> 06:44.409
Take care of your legs.

06:44.430 --> 06:45.510
Don't catch a cold.

06:51.070 --> 06:53.390
Are you so considerate to everyone?

06:54.030 --> 06:55.909
You are Master's family.

06:55.930 --> 06:57.370
Of course I should take good care of you.

06:57.930 --> 06:59.610
You are the young master of the Stone Clan.

06:59.630 --> 07:01.310
Why are you willing to join the Bright Moon Palace

07:01.340 --> 07:03.020
and be a guardian by Yue's side?

07:03.260 --> 07:05.160
I'm not the young master of the Stone Clan.

07:05.340 --> 07:07.380
I left the Stone Clan long ago.

07:08.510 --> 07:10.390
I had been wandering in the Demon Race at that time.

07:10.420 --> 07:12.010
Later, I met Master and helped him

07:12.430 --> 07:13.990
establish the Bright Moon Palace.

07:14.010 --> 07:15.490
Since then, I've had a place to stay.

07:16.030 --> 07:17.430
In the Demon Race, the strong prey on the weak.

07:17.550 --> 07:19.040
Without Master's protection,

07:19.280 --> 07:20.600
I'm afraid I would have been killed

07:20.600 --> 07:21.950
by other demons.

07:22.520 --> 07:23.750
Yue told me

07:23.880 --> 07:24.870
you left the Stone Clan

07:24.870 --> 07:26.600
because of something that happened in the clan before.

07:27.140 --> 07:28.840
You take so good care of me.

07:29.610 --> 07:30.880
Is it because

07:30.910 --> 07:31.850
you remember your father

07:31.880 --> 07:33.760
also broke a boy's legs?

07:39.570 --> 07:41.800
My father made such a mistake.

07:41.830 --> 07:42.730
So when I see you,

07:43.230 --> 07:44.909
I want to take good care of you.

07:47.930 --> 07:49.520
I can't walk.

07:49.659 --> 07:50.750
Please go get me

07:50.750 --> 07:52.120
the medicine in the cabinet.

07:52.820 --> 07:53.590
The cabinet?

07:57.870 --> 07:58.580
Okay.

08:05.490 --> 08:06.840
Sir, why are you laughing?

08:06.870 --> 08:09.010
Thinking about the gift you're about to receive

08:09.030 --> 08:10.790
fills me with excitement.

08:54.390 --> 08:55.340
Mother.

08:57.800 --> 08:58.640
Mother!

08:59.440 --> 09:01.310
She died long ago.

09:01.580 --> 09:03.810
How can you wake up a dead person?

09:06.120 --> 09:06.960
You

09:07.440 --> 09:08.720
killed my mother?

09:08.740 --> 09:10.100
Not just her.

09:10.130 --> 09:11.340
Your father too.

09:11.810 --> 09:13.120
And those members of the Stone Clan,

09:13.140 --> 09:14.590
all of you will be killed!

09:22.300 --> 09:24.000
I'm going to kill you!

09:30.950 --> 09:31.890
Why?

09:32.360 --> 09:34.280
There was no grudge between you and my parents.

09:34.900 --> 09:36.420
Why did you kill them?

09:36.480 --> 09:37.790
No grudge?

09:42.220 --> 09:43.500
Cang Shan,

09:43.970 --> 09:46.280
take a good look and see who I really am.

09:52.700 --> 09:53.580
You...

09:54.080 --> 09:55.050
What?

09:55.520 --> 09:56.880
My legs were broken beside the tombs.

09:56.960 --> 09:58.120
Your old friend has come back,

09:58.120 --> 09:59.390
but you can't recognize me?

10:03.630 --> 10:04.350
Father.

10:07.020 --> 10:08.100
I've thought it through.

10:08.640 --> 10:09.530
I'm not leaving.

10:10.080 --> 10:11.920
What... What do you want to do now?

10:11.940 --> 10:13.250
Since the Stone Clan is in danger,

10:13.280 --> 10:14.560
I must stay!

10:15.830 --> 10:17.790
You've spent your whole life working hard for the clan.

10:17.820 --> 10:19.510
Now you can live in seclusion comfortably

10:19.540 --> 10:20.730
in your old age.

10:20.750 --> 10:21.810
But I'm your son.

10:21.830 --> 10:22.870
I can't leave!

10:23.200 --> 10:23.990
Father,

10:24.010 --> 10:25.610
after I solve the crisis of the Stone Clan,

10:25.810 --> 10:27.000
I will take you home.

10:27.030 --> 10:27.980
Shut up!

10:28.140 --> 10:29.900
Who wants you to be a good person now?

10:30.990 --> 10:31.910
In this world,

10:31.910 --> 10:33.470
it's not just about being right or wrong.

10:33.770 --> 10:34.840
I said we should leave now.

10:34.860 --> 10:35.700
Then we must leave!

10:36.510 --> 10:37.460
Remember,

10:37.830 --> 10:39.500
being alive is more important than anything else.

10:40.840 --> 10:42.230
Even if you'll hate me in the future,

10:42.500 --> 10:44.040
I want you to live well.

10:44.250 --> 10:45.010
Father.

10:45.300 --> 10:45.750
Let's go!

10:45.750 --> 10:47.270
Your son is loyal and filial,

10:47.790 --> 10:49.870
but you are a coward.

10:50.010 --> 10:52.100
What a pity.

10:53.360 --> 10:53.960
You...

10:54.130 --> 10:55.650
What on earth happened in the Stone Clan

10:55.680 --> 10:56.920
back then?

10:57.390 --> 10:58.850
It makes you so scared.

11:01.430 --> 11:02.820
Why are you here?

11:02.930 --> 11:04.850
Master came all the way to the Stone Clan

11:04.870 --> 11:06.220
to help you find the murderer,

11:06.600 --> 11:08.330
but you want to leave without saying goodbye.

11:08.360 --> 11:10.530
Is this the Stone Clan's hospitality?

11:10.870 --> 11:12.350
I didn't invite you here.

11:13.000 --> 11:14.520
It's the Stone Clan's business.

11:14.670 --> 11:16.150
We'll handle it ourselves.

11:16.520 --> 11:17.960
You two, please go back.

11:20.590 --> 11:22.310
I'm going to ask you one last time.

11:22.690 --> 11:25.470
What on earth happened in the Stone Clan back then?

11:28.530 --> 11:29.530
Father,

11:29.550 --> 11:30.890
just tell them.

11:31.070 --> 11:32.350
Cang Shan said

11:32.370 --> 11:34.170
Master of Bright Moon is here to help us.

11:41.650 --> 11:42.760
The Stone Clan

11:44.080 --> 11:45.640
has always been kind to people.

11:47.780 --> 11:50.280
But if people know about that,

11:51.590 --> 11:54.160
no one will be willing to help the Stone Clan.

11:58.030 --> 12:00.820
The Stone Clan has always been solitary.

12:00.850 --> 12:02.060
We migrated, setting up camps

12:02.080 --> 12:03.280
wherever we stopped.

12:04.040 --> 12:05.100
That year,

12:05.610 --> 12:07.640
a devastating illness suddenly struck the clan.

12:07.660 --> 12:08.750
The patients' bones

12:08.790 --> 12:10.320
were as soft as mud.

12:10.500 --> 12:11.700
They couldn't stand.

12:11.780 --> 12:13.310
And their bodies were painful.

12:13.750 --> 12:15.270
Lei.

12:17.990 --> 12:19.360
Does it hurt a lot?

12:20.090 --> 12:21.410
Here. We've brought you medicine.

12:21.570 --> 12:22.290
You're back.

12:22.310 --> 12:23.140
Go.

12:23.170 --> 12:23.770
Help the clansmen

12:23.790 --> 12:25.390
take the medicine with warm water.

12:31.680 --> 12:32.930
This is...

12:36.970 --> 12:39.000
This is the medicine for treating the clansmen's illness.

12:39.370 --> 12:41.100
Are you going to watch

12:41.130 --> 12:42.530
our clansmen die?

12:43.950 --> 12:44.930
But this...

12:45.780 --> 12:46.570
Hurry up.

12:56.450 --> 12:57.300
I remember

12:57.330 --> 12:59.570
I was so sick that I couldn't walk.

12:59.590 --> 13:00.430
I thought

13:00.460 --> 13:01.890
I could never stand again in this life.

13:02.350 --> 13:04.030
But after taking the medicine Chief and the elders

13:04.030 --> 13:05.360
brought back in jars,

13:05.860 --> 13:06.990
I recovered.

13:07.760 --> 13:08.920
What was the medicine

13:08.940 --> 13:09.770
in the jars?

13:14.870 --> 13:16.210
Bones.

13:20.550 --> 13:23.000
We dug up the tombs of an ancient clan

13:23.780 --> 13:25.300
and ate their spiritual bones.

13:25.730 --> 13:26.770
What?

13:26.800 --> 13:28.800
The ancient clan was auspicious.

13:28.820 --> 13:30.230
Although they died,

13:30.260 --> 13:32.210
their bones still had spiritual energy

13:32.230 --> 13:33.470
and could heal bones.

13:33.780 --> 13:35.780
We had no choice at that time.

13:37.180 --> 13:38.790
That was the only way.

13:38.820 --> 13:39.710
Father,

13:39.990 --> 13:41.870
you were so silly!

13:42.310 --> 13:45.070
That's immoral,

13:45.100 --> 13:46.980
and we'll die a horrible death.

13:47.000 --> 13:48.120
I don't care!

13:49.200 --> 13:51.530
I just wanted you to survive!

13:52.030 --> 13:53.220
The Stone Clan

13:53.540 --> 13:55.940
has never killed anyone these years.

13:55.970 --> 13:57.830
Why should we be struck by such a deadly disease?

13:58.640 --> 14:01.000
We just unearthed the bones of the dead.

14:01.020 --> 14:02.220
They already died,

14:02.260 --> 14:03.390
but their spiritual bones

14:03.420 --> 14:05.660
could save every one of the Stone Clan.

14:05.680 --> 14:06.800
Why couldn't we eat them?

14:06.830 --> 14:08.110
Why couldn't we eat them?

14:10.220 --> 14:11.750
That's why the murderer

14:11.750 --> 14:13.930
broke the bones of those elders.

14:13.960 --> 14:15.410
It was a punishment,

14:15.430 --> 14:17.150
a ritual of revenge!

14:19.360 --> 14:20.840
He came to take revenge.

14:22.220 --> 14:24.220
He came for the whole Stone Clan.

14:25.760 --> 14:27.540
He came for Cang Shan.

14:28.100 --> 14:29.840
What does it have to do with Cang Shan?

14:31.100 --> 14:33.490
Back then, there was a boy of the ancient clan

14:33.900 --> 14:35.230
guarding the tombs.

14:35.270 --> 14:36.660
No outsiders were allowed to go near them.

14:36.710 --> 14:39.060
At that time, Cang Shan was in the maniac condition.

14:39.420 --> 14:41.550
He was delirious and couldn't control himself.

14:42.260 --> 14:43.070
So he...

14:44.330 --> 14:46.610
broke the boy's legs.

14:49.190 --> 14:51.730
What's the ancient clan

14:51.750 --> 14:52.960
that you just mentioned?

14:53.770 --> 14:54.930
The Baize Clan.

14:56.970 --> 14:58.060
What did you say?

14:58.850 --> 14:59.980
What did you say?

15:00.000 --> 15:01.010
Father!

15:01.350 --> 15:02.070
Master.

15:02.100 --> 15:02.900
Fan Yue,

15:02.920 --> 15:03.710
let go!

15:06.600 --> 15:07.650
Let go!

15:09.540 --> 15:10.340
Father.

15:11.730 --> 15:12.730
Father,

15:12.750 --> 15:14.030
are you alright?

15:16.780 --> 15:18.960
They went to the Baize Clan's ruins back then.

15:19.470 --> 15:21.670
The boy guarding the tombs was Qi Feng.

15:22.830 --> 15:23.870
If so...

15:25.050 --> 15:25.970
Oh no!

15:26.000 --> 15:26.790
Cang Shan!

15:31.150 --> 15:33.060
You're the boy of the ancient clan?

15:33.810 --> 15:34.610
Impossible.

15:35.280 --> 15:36.610
You already died.

15:36.630 --> 15:38.670
Of course you want me dead.

15:38.700 --> 15:39.700
If I die,

15:39.720 --> 15:41.920
no one will know the dirty thing the Stone Clan did.

15:43.210 --> 15:45.280
Did your parents ever tell you

15:45.300 --> 15:47.060
that the owner of that land,

15:47.080 --> 15:49.030
the ancient clan you spoke of,

15:49.060 --> 15:50.610
is the Baize Clan?

15:55.760 --> 15:56.760
Don't forget

15:57.100 --> 15:59.220
your master is also from the Baize Clan.

16:00.090 --> 16:01.920
If he knows what you did,

16:02.660 --> 16:03.740
do you think

16:03.760 --> 16:06.190
he'll destroy the Stone Clan himself or not?

16:12.260 --> 16:13.440
No.

16:15.700 --> 16:16.900
He won't.

16:17.050 --> 16:18.600
The Stone Clan did do something wrong,

16:18.620 --> 16:20.030
but not every one of the clan is guilty.

16:20.290 --> 16:21.560
In my eyes,

16:21.630 --> 16:24.060
no one from the Stone Clan is innocent!

16:25.440 --> 16:26.430
Right,

16:26.930 --> 16:28.570
I forgot to tell you something.

16:29.520 --> 16:31.470
I could control your father

16:31.490 --> 16:32.940
because back then,

16:32.970 --> 16:35.420
to suppress the monstrous power within you,

16:35.490 --> 16:38.270
he carved out his own demon core and gave it to you.

16:38.290 --> 16:40.020
To spare you from guilt,

16:40.050 --> 16:41.810
he altered your memories

16:41.830 --> 16:43.090
and took the blame

16:43.120 --> 16:44.870
for everything you did.

16:45.170 --> 16:46.300
What did you say?

16:46.690 --> 16:49.060
Such a moving father-son bond.

16:50.360 --> 16:52.320
It's so enviable.

16:52.840 --> 16:53.920
What demon core?

16:55.130 --> 16:56.440
What memory alteration?

16:57.130 --> 16:58.920
Since you don't remember anything,

17:00.060 --> 17:01.660
let me help you remember.

17:16.880 --> 17:18.050
You're not Yue.

17:18.069 --> 17:18.980
Who are you?

17:22.200 --> 17:23.310
What are you doing?

17:37.600 --> 17:38.730
-Cang Shan!
-This way!

17:38.760 --> 17:40.130
-Cang Shan!
-Cang Shan!

17:40.380 --> 17:42.280
-Cang Shan!
-Cang Shan!

17:42.790 --> 17:45.070
-Cang Shan! Calm down!
-Cang Shan!

17:45.110 --> 17:46.640
Cang Shan, what are you doing?

17:48.290 --> 17:49.250
What are you doing?

17:49.280 --> 17:50.180
Calm down!

17:54.550 --> 17:55.310
This...

18:04.260 --> 18:05.280
This...

18:15.290 --> 18:18.020
Your father's demon core is so bright.

18:18.360 --> 18:21.090
It's just like his love for his son.

18:23.400 --> 18:25.820
They're both disgusting.

18:58.610 --> 19:00.100
I'll kill you.

19:00.130 --> 19:01.760
I swear I'll kill you.

19:02.060 --> 19:03.550
I'll kill you.

19:05.820 --> 19:07.390
I'll kill you.

19:07.670 --> 19:09.880
I'll kill you!

19:13.080 --> 19:14.350
I'll kill you.

19:14.380 --> 19:16.130
I'll kill you!

19:17.000 --> 19:18.130
Kill.

19:25.900 --> 19:28.140
Help! Cang Shan wants to kill me!

19:28.170 --> 19:31.280
Help! Cang Shan wants to kill me!

19:34.740 --> 19:36.200
Look! Over there!

19:38.960 --> 19:39.790
Help!

19:40.960 --> 19:42.310
You... You...

19:43.350 --> 19:44.440
I'll kill you!

19:44.440 --> 19:46.830
I'll kill you. I'll kill you!

19:46.830 --> 19:48.080
-Help!
-What's going on?

19:48.730 --> 19:49.730
Hurry! Get up!

19:51.470 --> 19:54.090
-Let go!
-Kill him. Kill him.

19:54.760 --> 19:55.910
Hold him down!

19:56.020 --> 19:57.460
Young Chief went crazy.

19:57.640 --> 19:58.890
I saw him killing his mother.

19:58.910 --> 20:00.070
He wants to silence me.

20:00.100 --> 20:02.530
Kill him! Kill him!

20:03.260 --> 20:05.940
Kill him! I'll kill you!

20:05.960 --> 20:07.680
I'll kill you!

20:09.640 --> 20:12.360
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

20:12.400 --> 20:14.440
I'll kill you!

20:15.200 --> 20:16.270
Yeah.

20:16.270 --> 20:17.680
Burn him to death.

20:19.380 --> 20:20.300
Cang Shan!

20:20.330 --> 20:21.520
You killed your father and mother!

20:21.540 --> 20:22.740
You're unforgivable!

20:22.790 --> 20:23.970
He's a monster!

20:23.990 --> 20:25.080
Burn him!

20:25.110 --> 20:27.700
-Burn him! Burn him!
-Burn him! Burn him!

20:27.750 --> 20:30.000
It was Qi Feng! It was Qi Feng!

20:30.000 --> 20:31.960
He killed my parents and those clansmen!

20:31.960 --> 20:33.450
He is the murderer!

20:33.470 --> 20:34.470
He is!

20:34.500 --> 20:35.980
Qi Feng is disabled in both legs.

20:36.000 --> 20:37.000
His demonic power is weak.

20:37.020 --> 20:38.630
How could he possibly kill anyone?

20:38.660 --> 20:40.580
We saw you trying to silence him!

20:40.640 --> 20:42.800
At this point, you're still slandering him!

20:42.820 --> 20:43.540
Bastard!

20:43.570 --> 20:45.200
We won't trust you anymore!

20:45.220 --> 20:46.470
Burn him!

20:46.490 --> 20:50.070
-Burn him! Burn him!
-Burn him! Burn him!

20:50.090 --> 20:53.450
-Burn him! Burn him!
-Burn him! Burn him!

20:53.470 --> 20:55.570
-Burn him!
-Burn him!

20:55.600 --> 20:56.820
Stop!

20:56.890 --> 20:59.050
-Burn him!
-Burn him!

20:59.080 --> 21:00.530
Cang Shan is not the murderer.

21:00.550 --> 21:01.750
You can't kill him.

21:01.780 --> 21:02.880
Ms. Bai,

21:03.020 --> 21:05.020
we respect you because you and Master of Bright Moon are friends.

21:05.050 --> 21:05.960
These days,

21:05.980 --> 21:07.130
we have never restricted your movements.

21:07.160 --> 21:07.960
But today,

21:07.980 --> 21:09.790
it's the Stone Clan's own business.

21:09.820 --> 21:11.010
You'd better stay out of this!

21:11.030 --> 21:13.080
-Yes!
-You'd better stay out of this!

21:13.110 --> 21:15.030
Cang Shan is a member of the Bright Moon Palace.

21:15.060 --> 21:17.300
His business is the Bright Moon Palace's business.

21:17.320 --> 21:19.320
The clans in the demon realm don't interfere with each other.

21:19.350 --> 21:20.980
The Bright Moon Palace

21:21.000 --> 21:22.540
has gone too far by doing this!

21:23.410 --> 21:25.160
If you call this going too far,

21:25.360 --> 21:27.860
what should we call everything the Stone Clan did

21:27.880 --> 21:28.710
to the Baize Clan back then?

21:29.280 --> 21:32.110
Occupying the land, digging up the tombs,

21:32.130 --> 21:34.410
eating their bones, and suppressing their souls.

21:34.440 --> 21:35.850
Which of those isn't excessive?

21:36.250 --> 21:37.800
Which of those isn't a crime?

22:11.810 --> 22:13.730
I knew you would come to me.

22:14.220 --> 22:16.410
Is this the unspoken bond

22:16.430 --> 22:17.720
between brothers?

22:20.510 --> 22:21.310
Right,

22:22.330 --> 22:24.220
it's time to tell you my real identity.

22:25.650 --> 22:28.970
Greetings, Master of Bright Moon. I'm Chen Ye from the Cold Spring Palace.

22:34.280 --> 22:35.940
You did everything

22:36.420 --> 22:37.780
to the Stone Clan?

22:37.890 --> 22:39.650
You already have the answer in your heart.

22:39.790 --> 22:41.720
Do you have to ask me?

22:41.960 --> 22:42.900
Yes.

22:43.290 --> 22:45.780
Mr. Cang Sr., Mrs. Cang,

22:46.080 --> 22:47.510
and those elders

22:47.590 --> 22:48.960
were killed by me.

22:49.980 --> 22:51.090
Not just them.

22:51.110 --> 22:52.610
Everyone of the Stone Clan

22:52.760 --> 22:54.580
will be killed by me.

22:54.960 --> 22:56.400
The Stone Clan did do something wrong,

22:56.870 --> 22:58.360
but you shouldn't exterminate the whole clan.

22:58.940 --> 23:00.460
I shouldn't exterminate the whole clan?

23:00.960 --> 23:01.990
Master,

23:02.450 --> 23:04.530
you are so generous.

23:04.550 --> 23:05.900
For themselves, the Stone Clan

23:05.930 --> 23:07.410
took the Baize Clan's land and unearthed

23:07.430 --> 23:09.050
the bones of the Baize Clan's members as medicine.

23:09.500 --> 23:10.780
In order to conceal their crimes,

23:10.810 --> 23:11.810
they set up a stone formation

23:11.830 --> 23:13.950
to suppress the resentment aura of the Baize Clan.

23:14.120 --> 23:14.880
Fan Yue,

23:15.450 --> 23:17.630
what makes them less guilty?

23:17.700 --> 23:19.370
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

23:19.950 --> 23:20.830
If I had known earlier...

23:20.830 --> 23:21.590
If you had known earlier,

23:21.610 --> 23:23.130
would you destroy the Stone Clan?

23:24.360 --> 23:26.830
Just moments ago, you still told me

23:27.090 --> 23:29.020
the Stone Clan shouldn't be exterminated.

23:29.820 --> 23:30.740
Fan Yue,

23:31.600 --> 23:33.960
in this world, you're the last person qualified for avenging

23:33.980 --> 23:35.140
the Baize Clan.

23:35.880 --> 23:36.960
It was your birth

23:36.960 --> 23:39.260
that led to the Baize Clan's extermination.

23:39.370 --> 23:41.720
Without you, nothing would have happened.

23:42.060 --> 23:44.410
And I wouldn't have suffered so much.

23:45.110 --> 23:46.590
You asked me why just now.

23:47.690 --> 23:49.100
I also want to know why.

23:50.260 --> 23:52.130
Why was I the one who was abandoned

23:52.160 --> 23:53.680
-by Grandfather and the clansmen?
-Grandfather!

23:53.720 --> 23:56.310
Why was I the one whose legs were broken by Cang Shan?

23:56.310 --> 23:57.240
Why was I the one who survived

23:57.240 --> 23:59.430
like a stray dog?

23:59.680 --> 24:01.070
During those years of my greatest suffering,

24:01.110 --> 24:02.210
what were you doing?

24:02.260 --> 24:04.060
You were busy with your ambition,

24:04.090 --> 24:05.890
being Master of Bright Moon,

24:05.910 --> 24:07.720
and ruling the Polar Region!

24:08.380 --> 24:09.170
Fan Yue,

24:09.890 --> 24:11.610
what gives you the right to stand on the moral high ground

24:11.640 --> 24:13.440
to judge me?

24:17.440 --> 24:19.080
Don't listen to her nonsense!

24:19.430 --> 24:20.470
She's not one of us.

24:20.490 --> 24:21.690
How could she possibly know so much?

24:21.720 --> 24:22.240
Exactly.

24:22.260 --> 24:23.630
She must have made it up

24:23.660 --> 24:26.210
-to save Cang Shan!
-That's nonsense!

24:26.230 --> 24:27.690
You made it up!

24:27.720 --> 24:28.720
She didn't!

24:31.700 --> 24:33.810
What she just said is true.

24:34.760 --> 24:36.260
I was also involved

24:36.950 --> 24:38.350
in what happened back then.

24:38.370 --> 24:40.970
Chief, a few elders, and I

24:41.000 --> 24:42.840
dug up the tombs of the ancient clan,

24:42.870 --> 24:44.870
ground the bones into powder,

24:44.890 --> 24:45.860
added the powder to the medicine,

24:45.890 --> 24:47.960
and asked the sick clansmen to take it.

24:48.630 --> 24:49.500
It really happened?

24:49.550 --> 24:50.660
Is what he said true?

24:50.690 --> 24:51.650
This...

24:51.670 --> 24:52.820
It really happened?

24:53.250 --> 24:54.250
Everyone,

24:54.270 --> 24:56.670
this has nothing to do with Cang Shan.

24:56.700 --> 24:59.130
The boy from the Baize Clan didn't die back then.

24:59.150 --> 25:00.840
He's come to take revenge!

25:01.530 --> 25:03.010
-Take revenge?
-Take revenge?

25:03.740 --> 25:04.810
Cang Shan.

25:05.310 --> 25:06.030
Are you okay?

25:06.070 --> 25:07.680
He has killed so many people.

25:07.710 --> 25:08.990
He will kill me

25:09.010 --> 25:10.880
and all of us!

25:10.910 --> 25:13.470
I believe you don't truly want to kill Cang Shan.

25:14.020 --> 25:15.650
You were just so scared

25:15.890 --> 25:17.430
that you misjudged him.

25:17.950 --> 25:19.590
But this is unfair to Cang Shan.

25:20.180 --> 25:21.860
The grudge and hatred from the past

25:22.280 --> 25:23.690
shouldn't fall solely on his shoulders.

25:23.740 --> 25:24.540
That's right.

25:25.210 --> 25:26.720
Clansmen are also family.

25:26.750 --> 25:28.990
We can't abandon our family

25:29.010 --> 25:30.720
because of fear.

25:31.330 --> 25:32.380
Let Cang Shan go.

25:33.240 --> 25:34.160
That's right.

25:34.190 --> 25:35.300
We're family.

25:35.330 --> 25:36.610
Let him go.

25:36.800 --> 25:38.250
We can't let Cang Shan face it alone!

25:38.270 --> 25:39.870
Let him go!

25:39.900 --> 25:40.980
Let him go.

25:46.370 --> 25:47.770
Go to the Bright Moon Palace with me.

25:48.300 --> 25:50.010
Whether it's the past or present grudge,

25:50.700 --> 25:52.080
we need to put an end to it.

26:12.180 --> 26:13.350
Your legs...

26:13.590 --> 26:14.960
Why did I wait till now

26:14.960 --> 26:16.550
to take revenge on you and the Stone Clan?

26:17.090 --> 26:18.770
My legs were indeed broken.

26:18.790 --> 26:21.450
And I did suffer great pain and torture these years.

26:21.470 --> 26:24.480
Grand Master gave me a chance to stand again.

26:25.480 --> 26:27.640
Master, please allow me

26:27.660 --> 26:29.420
to send a big gift to Fan Yue

26:29.450 --> 26:30.920
and bring back the Contemplation Stone.

26:32.740 --> 26:35.060
I've always been fair in rewarding and punishing people.

26:35.390 --> 26:37.290
Since you have successfully cultivated evil insects

26:37.750 --> 26:40.260
and want to help me bring back the Contemplation Stone,

26:40.290 --> 26:41.530
I'll

26:42.360 --> 26:44.900
help you fulfill a wish too.

26:52.620 --> 26:53.710
My legs...

27:12.750 --> 27:13.550
Come on.

27:13.800 --> 27:14.920
Try to stand.

27:27.020 --> 27:27.820
Come on.

27:36.870 --> 27:37.840
Come on.

27:47.600 --> 27:48.480
How are you feeling?

27:49.230 --> 27:50.430
Thank you, Master.

27:51.130 --> 27:52.800
I won't let you down.

27:54.150 --> 27:54.950
Remember,

27:55.390 --> 27:57.740
people are not afraid of never possessing something,

27:57.780 --> 27:58.980
but of

27:59.010 --> 28:00.750
losing it

28:01.090 --> 28:02.540
after having it.

28:04.140 --> 28:04.940
Chen Ye,

28:05.980 --> 28:08.200
I want you to remember

28:08.220 --> 28:10.070
the feeling of standing.

28:10.160 --> 28:12.010
I hope you

28:12.590 --> 28:14.830
won't lose it.

28:15.720 --> 28:16.520
Yes,

28:18.080 --> 28:19.070
Master.

28:23.780 --> 28:25.100
The spiritual veins in your legs were broken.

28:25.190 --> 28:26.760
The power of eternals or demons can't cure you.

28:26.780 --> 28:28.020
You're doubting the power

28:28.050 --> 28:29.840
of my grand master because you can't do that?

28:29.860 --> 28:31.250
If he had such power,

28:31.310 --> 28:32.550
I would have certainly noticed it.

28:32.580 --> 28:34.340
Grand Master has lived for 1,000 years.

28:34.360 --> 28:35.630
How can you know

28:35.660 --> 28:37.200
all of his secret techniques?

28:37.330 --> 28:38.410
Have you ever thought about this?

28:39.060 --> 28:40.330
You've been in the Cold Spring Palace for many years.

28:40.360 --> 28:41.240
Since he has a way,

28:41.240 --> 28:42.440
why didn't he cure you earlier?

28:43.520 --> 28:44.670
Zhen Yu has ulterior motives.

28:44.690 --> 28:45.690
He's not a good person.

28:45.720 --> 28:47.180
Everything gained comes with a price.

28:47.340 --> 28:49.740
Qi Feng, don't be controlled by him.

28:49.770 --> 28:51.200
I don't need you to tell me if I'm

28:51.220 --> 28:52.510
controlled by Grand Master.

28:52.710 --> 28:55.040
But tonight in the Stone Clan,

28:55.130 --> 28:57.610
everyone is under my control.

29:23.980 --> 29:24.780
Release Cang Shan.

29:24.800 --> 29:26.040
Let him go.

29:26.070 --> 29:28.020
-Let him go.
-Yes.

29:29.790 --> 29:31.440
-We're family.
-Yeah.

29:41.890 --> 29:43.290
What's wrong with them?

29:43.650 --> 29:44.860
It's the evil insects.

29:44.890 --> 29:47.360
Qi Feng is using the evil insects to control every one of the Stone Clan.

29:50.100 --> 29:51.910
Do you think I came to the Stone Clan

29:51.940 --> 29:54.050
just to act with you?

29:54.290 --> 29:55.850
Before you entered the Stone Clan,

29:55.870 --> 29:57.910
I had already planted an evil insect

29:57.940 --> 29:59.100
in every one of the Stone Clan.

29:59.160 --> 30:00.920
Everyone's life is in my hands,

30:01.380 --> 30:02.710
including yours.

30:02.740 --> 30:04.200
When did you plant it in me?

30:04.370 --> 30:06.290
When your guilt towards me was at its peak

30:06.320 --> 30:08.160
and before you suspected me,

30:08.180 --> 30:11.580
I put it in the food I personally prepared for you.

30:17.630 --> 30:20.390
You're Demon King of the Polar Region and Master of Bright Moon.

30:20.610 --> 30:22.970
Ordinary evil insects won't work on you.

30:23.130 --> 30:24.930
The parent insect in your body

30:24.960 --> 30:26.920
was specially cultivated for you.

30:28.030 --> 30:30.150
No matter how powerful you are,

30:30.180 --> 30:33.210
you can't resist the invasion of the parent insect.

30:34.400 --> 30:36.250
Evil insects can't be extracted.

30:36.440 --> 30:38.010
You can't neutralize it

30:38.140 --> 30:40.090
unless you die.

31:32.870 --> 31:34.460
Bai Shuo, how are you?

31:34.490 --> 31:35.580
I'm fine.

31:35.610 --> 31:38.330
It's just that I've used too much spiritual power and temporarily lost my strength.

31:55.780 --> 31:56.570
Bai Shuo,

31:56.980 --> 31:58.700
did you see something again?

31:58.730 --> 31:59.880
The stone formation.

32:00.490 --> 32:02.100
The stone formation is about to explode.

32:02.220 --> 32:03.980
The Baize Clan's resentment aura is about to be unleashed.

32:08.880 --> 32:10.560
The Baize Clan's resentment aura hates the Stone Clan.

32:10.580 --> 32:11.450
Once it's unleashed,

32:11.470 --> 32:12.680
plus Qi Feng's evil insects,

32:13.160 --> 32:14.330
the Stone Clan will surely perish.

32:15.270 --> 32:17.580
Bai Shuo, you go meet up with Master first.

32:18.160 --> 32:20.200
This is the grudge we brought upon ourselves.

32:20.220 --> 32:21.220
I'll deal with it.

32:22.160 --> 32:22.880
It's dangerous.

32:24.540 --> 32:25.600
Bai Shuo,

32:26.120 --> 32:27.660
today, I finally realized

32:28.050 --> 32:30.050
my parents had been protecting me.

32:30.930 --> 32:32.330
But apart from disobeying them,

32:32.860 --> 32:34.000
I have never fulfilled my responsibility

32:34.000 --> 32:35.240
as the young master of the Stone Clan.

32:36.070 --> 32:38.090
Now that my parents are gone,

32:38.540 --> 32:40.420
I should be responsible for the Stone Clan.

32:41.760 --> 32:43.780
I can't let anything happen to my clansmen again.

32:47.780 --> 32:48.580
Go to Master.

32:48.610 --> 32:49.720
Don't let anything happen to him!

32:50.460 --> 32:51.350
Cang Shan!

32:56.580 --> 32:57.790
Fan Yue.

33:03.890 --> 33:06.220
You think you can save Cang Shan

33:06.250 --> 33:08.010
by splitting up from Bai Shuo?

33:08.710 --> 33:09.960
Fan Yue,

33:10.210 --> 33:13.090
I want you to kill Cang Shan personally.

33:33.250 --> 33:34.350
Your legs...

33:35.290 --> 33:37.260
You really are the person he likes.

33:37.530 --> 33:39.540
Even your reaction of surprise is the same.

33:39.850 --> 33:41.040
Where is Fan Yue?

33:41.280 --> 33:42.430
What did you do to him?

33:42.450 --> 33:44.130
He has become my weapon.

33:44.160 --> 33:46.470
He will help me kill everyone I want to kill.

33:47.140 --> 33:48.570
Starting...

33:48.600 --> 33:50.110
with Cang Shan.

33:50.880 --> 33:52.380
With his brother's blood on his hands,

33:52.400 --> 33:54.030
I really want to see

33:54.160 --> 33:55.440
how he will react

33:55.460 --> 33:56.870
when he regains his senses.

33:57.290 --> 33:59.200
You said you don't hate him.

33:59.340 --> 34:01.040
So it was a lie from the beginning.

34:01.450 --> 34:03.160
Since you were forced to take his place back then,

34:03.180 --> 34:04.660
you've been holding a grudge.

34:04.690 --> 34:06.150
Shouldn't I?

34:06.210 --> 34:08.080
I've never experienced what you've been through,

34:08.290 --> 34:09.679
so I'm in no position to speak.

34:09.800 --> 34:11.800
But when you were taken away by the Tiger Clan,

34:11.820 --> 34:13.370
it wasn't what Fan Yue wanted either.

34:13.780 --> 34:14.929
You lost your clansmen,

34:14.960 --> 34:16.889
but so did he.

34:17.510 --> 34:18.590
All these years,

34:18.610 --> 34:19.659
he's felt guilty

34:19.690 --> 34:21.120
and never had peace.

34:21.510 --> 34:22.800
The truth is in this world,

34:23.260 --> 34:25.850
you're not the only one living in pain.

34:25.880 --> 34:26.810
Yeah.

34:27.320 --> 34:29.290
I'm not the only one in this world in misery

34:29.449 --> 34:30.440
and pain.

34:30.880 --> 34:32.260
But why

34:32.469 --> 34:33.550
is he always protected

34:33.570 --> 34:34.659
and chosen?

34:35.420 --> 34:36.360
And I

34:36.530 --> 34:39.139
can only be abandoned and maltreated.

34:39.170 --> 34:40.949
And I could only make myself

34:40.980 --> 34:43.300
a disgusting monster to survive!

34:44.110 --> 34:45.120
But he

34:45.179 --> 34:47.889
is Demon King of the Polar Region and Master of Bright Moon.

34:47.920 --> 34:49.480
All the demons submit to him.

34:50.380 --> 34:52.340
How much pain could he really feel?

34:53.270 --> 34:54.980
Fan Yue's demonic power

34:55.010 --> 34:56.540
was bought with his lifespan.

34:57.380 --> 35:00.440
All these years, he's come this far, risking his own life,

35:00.740 --> 35:02.750
just to avenge the Baize Clan

35:02.770 --> 35:04.000
and find you.

35:04.110 --> 35:05.880
But all you give him in return is hatred.

35:06.670 --> 35:08.300
Isn't he pathetic?

35:08.330 --> 35:09.930
What do you mean by saying his demonic power

35:09.950 --> 35:11.280
was bought with his lifespan?

35:11.310 --> 35:12.610
How could a boy

35:12.750 --> 35:14.740
become Demon King of the Polar Region

35:14.760 --> 35:16.200
within just a few years?

35:16.810 --> 35:18.650
In order to improve his demonic power quickly,

35:18.680 --> 35:19.760
he forced himself to practice

35:19.780 --> 35:21.050
and suffered a backlash.

35:21.080 --> 35:22.800
He's been tortured by the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal.

35:23.210 --> 35:24.330
The stronger he is,

35:24.360 --> 35:25.840
the closer he is to death.

35:26.700 --> 35:28.930
Why do you think he wants to activate the Contemplation Stone?

35:29.970 --> 35:32.180
Because only the divine power of the Contemplation Stone

35:32.320 --> 35:33.690
can save his life!

35:33.710 --> 35:34.540
No!

35:34.810 --> 35:35.850
You're lying to me.

35:36.280 --> 35:37.160
He's Demon King.

35:37.190 --> 35:38.550
Why would he sacrifice his life

35:38.590 --> 35:39.900
to avenge the Baize Clan

35:39.920 --> 35:41.930
and find me, whose fate was uncertain?

35:42.310 --> 35:43.900
I've endured humiliation

35:43.930 --> 35:45.740
in the Cold Spring Palace for so many years

35:46.450 --> 35:48.050
just to destroy the Stone Clan

35:48.510 --> 35:50.040
and kill Fan Yue.

35:50.810 --> 35:52.090
I can't be wrong.

35:52.940 --> 35:55.070
I came here by Grand Master's command.

35:55.310 --> 35:57.540
I must take the Contemplation Stone back.

35:58.430 --> 35:59.680
Bai Shuo,

35:59.700 --> 36:01.220
you can't escape.

36:12.760 --> 36:15.180
The stone pillars show no sign of exploding.

36:19.120 --> 36:20.720
It's too late

36:20.740 --> 36:21.780
to escape now.

36:47.520 --> 36:49.290
Yue, don't go.

36:49.550 --> 36:50.590
Yue.

36:51.320 --> 36:53.130
Don't be angry, Yue.

36:53.150 --> 36:54.230
It's my fault.

36:54.330 --> 36:56.080
I shouldn't have teased you and Mei.

36:56.590 --> 36:58.880
Grandfather asked someone to make a new nameplate for you.

36:58.900 --> 37:00.960
But their craftsmanship is not as good as mine.

37:01.030 --> 37:02.600
I made this myself.

37:02.040 --> 37:05.790
[Fan Yue]

37:02.630 --> 37:03.790
Consider it my way of saying sorry.

37:04.420 --> 37:05.910
Don't be angry, okay?

37:06.520 --> 37:08.040
I forgive you this time.

37:08.060 --> 37:09.190
Don't do it again.

37:13.460 --> 37:18.420
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

37:20.960 --> 37:22.530
I'm going to say it again!

37:21.580 --> 37:27.200
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

37:22.850 --> 37:26.240
Hand over the child with purple pupils!

37:29.900 --> 37:37.300
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

37:38.230 --> 37:43.410
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

37:39.640 --> 37:42.040
Why have Qi Feng's eyes become purple?

37:42.070 --> 37:44.230
Grandfather, don't hand over Qi Feng.

37:44.360 --> 37:46.420
Qi Feng! Qi Feng!

37:45.600 --> 37:49.960
♫Across thousands of miles♫

37:46.790 --> 37:48.200
Grandfather, why?

37:48.230 --> 37:50.440
-Qi Feng!
-Grandfather, why?

37:50.740 --> 37:53.410
The child you ask for is here.

37:54.550 --> 37:59.340
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

37:55.210 --> 37:56.000
Good.

37:56.430 --> 37:57.740
-Come here!
-Qi Feng!

37:58.160 --> 37:59.040
Qi Feng!

37:59.070 --> 38:01.150
Grandfather, why?

38:01.190 --> 38:02.340
Qi Feng!

38:02.940 --> 38:04.020
No!

38:04.040 --> 38:05.410
-Qi Feng!
-Grandfather!

38:05.480 --> 38:08.600
Why? Why?

38:11.580 --> 38:16.990
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

38:14.730 --> 38:17.290
All of you are dead.

38:17.370 --> 38:19.310
I risked my life to escape from the Tiger Clan.

38:19.480 --> 38:21.770
I haven't got the answer from you.

38:19.660 --> 38:25.270
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

38:21.790 --> 38:23.670
How could you all be dead?

38:24.300 --> 38:26.770
You abandoned me.

38:26.940 --> 38:28.230
Who should I

38:27.850 --> 38:35.120
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

38:28.260 --> 38:30.010
hold accountable for this?

38:30.640 --> 38:32.270
How could you be dead?

38:32.300 --> 38:34.110
How could you be dead?

38:34.260 --> 38:36.260
How could you be dead?

38:35.650 --> 38:40.640
♫I'm your wanderer♫

38:36.290 --> 38:39.470
How could you be dead?

38:41.070 --> 38:43.790
How could you be dead?

38:54.560 --> 38:55.480
Yue.

39:05.430 --> 39:06.360
Why...

39:06.740 --> 39:07.600
is...

39:07.620 --> 39:09.580
is there no Yue's tombstone?

39:10.270 --> 39:11.440
He's not dead.

39:11.590 --> 39:12.940
Yue is still alive!

39:41.210 --> 39:42.160
Yue.

39:45.850 --> 39:47.080
You are not Yue.

39:47.100 --> 39:48.210
Who are you?

39:50.400 --> 39:51.500
What are you doing?

40:22.040 --> 40:23.440
You don't want to accept this?

40:25.280 --> 40:26.620
I can help you.

40:28.150 --> 40:31.150
But I don't like weak people.

40:32.110 --> 40:34.720
I will become a strong person.

40:57.510 --> 40:58.400
Zhen Yu?

41:01.100 --> 41:02.640
This is the Cold Spring Palace.

41:02.940 --> 41:04.250
From today onwards,

41:04.660 --> 41:06.050
your name

41:06.080 --> 41:07.480
will be Chen Ye.

41:08.610 --> 41:09.890
Thank you, Master.

41:10.190 --> 41:11.580
So he is the legendary

41:11.610 --> 41:13.010
Lord Chen Ye

41:13.030 --> 41:13.760
from the Cold Spring Palace.

41:13.790 --> 41:16.020
You all have your own reasons for joining me.

41:16.040 --> 41:17.530
But the Cold Spring Palace is no place for charity.

41:17.560 --> 41:20.070
You have to shed all your

41:20.220 --> 41:22.780
hesitation and weakness,

41:22.800 --> 41:24.530
and become the strongest one

41:24.620 --> 41:27.300
and someone useful to me.

41:28.370 --> 41:29.630
Otherwise,

41:29.860 --> 41:32.850
you know what will happen.

41:33.720 --> 41:34.760
You may leave.

41:34.780 --> 41:36.740
-Yes, Master.
-Yes, Master.

41:55.790 --> 41:56.590
Xi?

42:02.770 --> 42:03.670
Xi.

42:03.690 --> 42:05.650
Didn't you go traveling with Taoists?

42:05.680 --> 42:07.450
Why were you in the Cold Spring Palace?

42:07.480 --> 42:08.480
Xi!

42:11.510 --> 42:12.790
Xi!

42:20.750 --> 42:21.820
Xi!

42:22.220 --> 42:23.390
Xi!

42:25.310 --> 42:26.350
Xi!

42:29.250 --> 42:30.290
The power of the Contemplation Stone

42:30.320 --> 42:32.280
actually can help you see my memories.

42:32.960 --> 42:34.250
What did you see?

42:35.070 --> 42:36.990
Why is Xi in your memories?

42:37.010 --> 42:38.560
Why was she in the Cold Spring Palace?

42:38.930 --> 42:40.140
What Xi?

42:40.170 --> 42:41.480
When you were given the name by Zhen Yu,

42:41.500 --> 42:43.100
there was a girl with you in the palace.

42:43.130 --> 42:43.900
Where is she?

42:47.070 --> 42:49.020
You want to know where she is?

42:49.050 --> 42:50.030
Sure.

42:50.260 --> 42:51.810
Go to the Cold Spring Palace with me.

42:51.840 --> 42:53.000
Once Fan Yue is dead,

42:53.030 --> 42:54.440
the Cold Spring Palace will hold a dominant position.

42:54.600 --> 42:56.370
Maybe Grand Master will spare your life

42:56.440 --> 42:57.480
if he's in a good mood.

42:58.310 --> 43:01.060
You keep saying you want to kill Fan Yue.

43:02.090 --> 43:03.570
But do you really hate him that much?

43:06.180 --> 43:07.820
Just now in your memories,

43:07.850 --> 43:09.770
I saw some other images.

43:11.050 --> 43:13.890
Qi Feng, remember,

43:16.160 --> 43:19.620
Yue was born extraordinary.

43:19.920 --> 43:22.820
He is not only your brother,

43:23.360 --> 43:24.570
but also

43:24.820 --> 43:28.020
someone you should protect with your life.

43:28.350 --> 43:29.350
Grandfather,

43:29.720 --> 43:31.280
who on earth is Yue?

43:31.750 --> 43:33.520
His identity

43:33.760 --> 43:35.720
can't be revealed.

43:36.060 --> 43:38.460
But you must promise me

43:38.490 --> 43:42.090
you'll protect him.

43:43.810 --> 43:45.930
I will protect Yue.

43:46.360 --> 43:48.320
I'll protect him with my life.

43:50.850 --> 43:51.760
So,

43:52.030 --> 43:54.550
when you were handed over to the Tiger Clan by your grandfather,

43:55.570 --> 43:57.730
and when you were imprisoned by the Tiger Clan,

43:57.750 --> 44:00.320
you were confused and scared,

44:00.560 --> 44:01.810
but you never told them

44:01.840 --> 44:03.640
Fan Yue was the boy with purple pupils.

44:03.660 --> 44:04.780
Qi Feng,

44:05.460 --> 44:07.750
you don't really hate Fan Yue, do you?
